RENGAR.description: Rengar roars, deals magic damage, and heals himself for some of the damage taken. Ferocity: Rengar deals magic damage and instead of partially healing himself gains movement speed and removes all crowd control effects from himself.

RENGAR.name: BOLA STRIKE
RENGAR.description: Rengar throws a bola causing physical damage and slows his enemy for a couple seconds. Ferocity: Rengar gains even more movement speed and roots his enemy instead of slowing them.

RENGAR.name: THRILL OF THE HUNT
RENGAR.description: Rengar gains movement speed and reveals the nearest enemy champion for a period of time. Shortly after casting Rengar becomes camoflauged with his next attack shredding the target's armor for a period of time.

RIVEN.name: RUNIC BLADE
RIVEN.description: Riven's abilities charge her blade, and her basic attacks expend charges to deal an additional damage.

RIVEN.name: BROKEN WINGS
RIVEN.description: Riven lashes out in a series of strikes. This ability can be reactivated three times in a short time frame with the third hit knocking back nearby enemies.

RIVEN.name: KI BURST
RIVEN.description: Riven emits a Ki Burst, damaging and stunning nearby enemies.

RIVEN.name: VALOR
RIVEN.description: Riven steps forward a short distance and blocks incoming damage.

RIVEN.name: BLADE OF THE EXILE
RIVEN.description: Riven empowers her keepsake weapon with energy, and gains Attack Damage and Range. During this time, she also gains the ability to use Wind Slash, a powerful ranged attack, once.

SAMIRA.name: DAREDEVIL IMPULSE
SAMIRA.description: Samira builds a combo by hitting attacks or abilities unique from the previous hit. Samira's attacks in melee range deal additional magic damage. Samira's attacks against enemies affected by Immobilizing effects will dash her to her attack range. If the enemy is Knocked Up, she also keeps them Knocked Up briefly.

SAMIRA.name: FLAIR
SAMIRA.description: Samira fires a shot or swings her sword, dealing damage. If cast during Wild Rush, strike all enemies in her path upon completion.

SAMIRA.name: BLADE WHIRL
SAMIRA.description: Samira slashes around her, damaging enemies and destroying enemy missiles.

SAMIRA.name: WILD RUSH
SAMIRA.description: Samira dashes through an enemy (including structures), slashing enemies she passes through and gaining Attack Speed. Killing an enemy champion refreshes this ability's cooldown.

SAMIRA.name: INFERNO TRIGGER
SAMIRA.description: Samira unleashes a torrent of shots from her weapons, wildly shooting all enemies surrounding her.

SENNA.name: ABSOLUTION
SENNA.description: When units die near Senna, their souls are periodically trapped by the Black Mist. Senna can attack these souls to free them, absorbing the Mist that held them in death. Mist fuels her Relic Cannon's power with increased Attack Damage, Attack Range, and Critical Strike Chance. Attacks from Senna's Relic Cannon take longer to fire, deals bonus damage , and briefly grant her a portion of her target's Movement Speed.

SENNA.name: PIERCING DARKNESS
SENNA.description: Piercing Darkness’s cast range matches Senna’s attack range and its cast time is improved with Attack Speed. It can target anything and applies on-hit effects to enemy champions.

SENNA.name: LAST EMBRACE
SENNA.description: Senna sends forth a wave of Black Mist. If it hits an enemy it latches onto them hungrily, rooting them and everything nearby after a brief delay.

SENNA.name: CURSE OF THE BLACK MIST
SENNA.description: Senna draws the Mist she has stored in her weapon into a storm around her, embracing darkness and becoming a wraith within. Allies who enter the area are camouflaged and also appear as wraiths as the Mist shrouds them. Wraiths gain increased movement speed, are unselectable, and hide their identities.

SENNA.name: DAWNING SHADOW
SENNA.description: Senna calls upon the relic stones of fallen Sentinels, splitting her relic cannon into a holy array of shadow and light. She then fires a global beam that shields allies from harm, while damaging enemies caught in the center.

SERAPHINE.name: STAGE PRESENCE
SERAPHINE.description: Every third ability cast will Echo, casting it again. Casting Seraphine's abilities grants a Note to nearby allies. For each Note, Seraphine's next basic attack gains Attack Range and bonus damage.

SERAPHINE.name: HIGH NOTE
SERAPHINE.description: Seraphine deals damage in an area, increased by enemies' missing Health.

SERAPHINE.name: SURROUND SOUND
SERAPHINE.description: Seraphine shields all nearly ally champions and grants them Movement Speed. If Seraphine is already shielded, nearby allies are healed, increasing for each ally.

SERAPHINE.name: BEAT DROP
SERAPHINE.description: Seraphine deals damage and slows enemies. If the enemy is already slowed, they are rooted instead. If they are already rooted, they are stunned instead.

SERAPHINE.name: ENCORE
SERAPHINE.description: Seraphine deals damage in a line, charming and slowing enemies. Encore extends if it touches an ally or enemy champion.

SETT.name: PIT GRIT
SETT.description: Sett's basic attacks alternate between left and right punch. Right punch is slightly stronger and faster. Sett also hates losing, gaining additional health regeneration based off of his missing health.

SETT.name: KNUCKLE DOWN
SETT.description: Sett's next two attacks deal additional damage based off of the target's max health. Sett also gains movement speed while moving towards enemy champions.

SETT.name: HAYMAKER
SETT.description: Sett passively stores damage he takes as Grit. On cast, Sett expends all stored Grit to gain a shield and punch an area, dealing true damage in the center and physical damage on the sides.

SETT.name: FACEBREAKER
SETT.description: Sett pulls in all enemies on opposite sides of him, dealing damage and stunning them. If enemies were only on one side, they are slowed instead of stunned.

SETT.name: THE SHOW STOPPER
SETT.description: Sett carries an enemy champion through the air and slams them into the ground, dealing damage and slowing all enemies near where they land.

SHEN.name: KI BARRIER
SHEN.description: After casting a spell, Shen gets a shield. Affecting other champions reduces the cooldown of this effect.

SHEN.name: TWILIGHT ASSAULT
SHEN.description: Shen recalls his spirit blade to attack with it, dealing damage based on the target's max health. The attacks are greatly empowered if it collides with an enemy champion, and all collided enemies are slowed while running away from Shen.

SHEN.name: SPIRIT'S REFUGE
SHEN.description: Shen sends his spirit blade to an ally, creating a zone that blocks enemy attacks.

SHEN.name: SHADOW DASH
SHEN.description: Shen dashes in a direction, taunting enemies in his path

SHEN.name: STAND UNITED
SHEN.description: Shen shields target allied champion from incoming damage, and soon after teleports to their location.

SHYVANA.name: FURY OF THE DRAGONBORN
SHYVANA.description: Shyvana gains stacks when slaying large and epic monsters, as well as champions. Dragons grant extra stacks. Every 100 stack enhances one of Shyvana's abilities.

SHYVANA.name: TWIN BITE
SHYVANA.description: Shyvana strikes twice on her next attack. Basic attacks reduce the cooldown of Twin Bite. Dragon Form: Twin Bite cleaves all units in front of Shyvana. Slaying Mountain Drake causes Twin Bite to slow enemies while in Dragon Form.

SHYVANA.name: BURNOUT
SHYVANA.description: Shyvana surrounds herself in fire, dealing magic damage per second to nearby enemies and moving faster for 3 seconds. The Movement Speed reduces over the duration of the spell. Basic attacks extend the duration of Burnout. Dragon Form: Burnout grows in size. Slaying Cloud Drake gives Shyvana 25% extra Movement Speed while in Dragon Form.

SHYVANA.name: FLAME BREATH
SHYVANA.description: Shyvana unleashes a fireball that deals damage to all enemies it encounters and leaves cinders on the target, marking them for 5 seconds. Shyvana's basic attacks on marked targets deal a percentage of their maximum Health as damage on-hit. Dragon Form: Flame Breath explodes on impact or at target location, dealing bonus damage and scorching the earth for a short duration. Slaying Infernal Drake converts damage dealt to marked enemies to true damage while in Dragon Form.

SHYVANA.name: DRAGON'S DESCENT
SHYVANA.description:
Shyvana transforms into a dragon and takes flight to a target location. Enemies along her path take damage and are knocked toward her target location. 

Shyvana passively gains Fury per second and gains 2 Fury on basic attack.

SINGED.name: NOXIOUS SLIPSTREAM
SINGED.description: Singed drafts off nearby champions, gaining a burst of movement speed when passing them.

SINGED.name: POISON TRAIL
SINGED.description: Leaves a trail of poison behind Singed, dealing damage to enemies caught in the path.

SINGED.name: MEGA ADHESIVE
SINGED.description: Throws a vial of mega adhesive on the ground, slowing and grounding enemies who walk on it.

SINGED.name: FLING
SINGED.description: Damages target enemy unit and flings them into the air behind Singed. If the target Singed flings lands in his Mega Adhesive, they are also rooted.

SINGED.name: INSANITY POTION
SINGED.description: Singed drinks a potent brew of chemicals, granting him increased combat stats.

SION.name: GLORY IN DEATH
SION.description: After being killed, Sion will temporarily reanimate with rapidly decaying Health. His attacks become very rapid, heal him, and deal bonus damage based on his target's maximum Health.

SION.name: DECIMATING SMASH
SION.description: Sion charges a powerful swing in an area in front of himself that will deal damage to enemies when released. If he charges for enough time, enemies hit by the swing will also be knocked up and stunned.

SION.name: SOUL FURNACE
SION.description: Sion shields himself and can reactivate after 3 seconds to deal Magic Damage to enemies nearby. When Sion kills enemies, he passively gains maximum Health.

SION.name: ROAR OF THE SLAYER
SION.description: Sion fires a short range shockwave that damages and slows and reduces the Armor of the first enemy hit. If the shockwave hits a minion or monster, it will be knocked back, damaging, slowing, and reducing the Armor of all enemies that it passes through.

SION.name: UNSTOPPABLE ONSLAUGHT
SION.description: Sion charges in a direction, ramping up speed over time. He can steer his charge slightly with the mouse cursor location. When he collides with an enemy he deals damage and knocks them up based on the distance he has charged.

SIVIR.name: FLEET OF FOOT
SIVIR.description: Sivir gains a short burst of Move Speed when she attacks an enemy champion.

SIVIR.name: BOOMERANG BLADE
SIVIR.description: Sivir hurls her crossblade like a boomerang, dealing damage each way.

SIVIR.name: RICOCHET
SIVIR.description: Sivir's next few basic attacks gain additional attack speed and bounce to nearby targets, dealing reduced damage while bouncing.

SIVIR.name: SPELL SHIELD
SIVIR.description: Creates a magical barrier that blocks a single enemy ability cast on Sivir. She receives health and a burst of movement speed if a spell is blocked.

SIVIR.name: ON THE HUNT
SIVIR.description: Sivir leads her allies in battle, granting them a burst of move speed for a short time. In addition, her ability cooldowns are reduced. Sivir gains morale when damaging an enemy, granting a buff to allies and refreshing her ultimate at max morale.

SONA.name: POWER CHORD
SONA.description: After 3 spell casts, Sona's next attack will deal bonus magic damage and stun the target.

SONA.name: HYMN OF VALOR
SONA.description: Sona plays the Hymn of Valor, sends out bolts of sound, dealing magic damage to two nearby enemies, prioritizing champions and monsters. Sona gains a temporary aura that grants allies tagged by the zone bonus damage on their next attack against enemies.

SONA.name: ARIA OF PERSEVERANCE
SONA.description: Sona plays the Aria of Perseverance, sending out protective melodies, healing Sona and a nearby wounded ally. Sona gains a temporary aura that grants allies tagged by the zone a temporary shield.

SONA.name: SONG OF CELERITY
SONA.description: Sona plays the Song of Celerity, granting nearby allies bonus Movement Speed. Sona gains a temporary aura that grants allied champions tagged by the zone bonus Movement Speed.

SONA.name: CRESCENDO
SONA.description: Passive: Sona’s halo strengthens, providing higher buffs. Sona’s ultimate chord advances slowly to the target point, dealing damage on its way. Every enemy hit for the first time is stunned.

SORAKA.name: SALVATION
SORAKA.description: Soraka runs faster towards nearby low health allies.

SORAKA.name: STARCALL
SORAKA.description: A star falls from the sky at the target location dealing magic damage and slowing enemies. If an enemy champion is hit by Starcall, Soraka recovers Health.

SORAKA.name: ASTRAL INFUSION
SORAKA.description: Soraka sacrifices a portion of her own health to heal another friendly champion.

SORAKA.name: EQUINOX
SORAKA.description: Creates a zone at a location that silences all enemies inside. When the zone expires, all enemies still inside are rooted.

SORAKA.name: WISH
SORAKA.description: Soraka fills her allies with hope, instantly restoring health to herself and all friendly champions.

SWAIN.name: RAVENOUS FLOCK
SWAIN.description: Swain's ravens collect Soul Fragments that heal him and permanently increase his maximum health.

SWAIN.name: DEATH'S HAND
SWAIN.description: Swain unleashes several bolts of eldritch power that pierce through enemies. Enemies hit take more damage for each bolt they are struck by.

SWAIN.name: VISION OF EMPIRE
SWAIN.description: Swain opens a demon eye that deals damage and slows enemies. Champions hit are revealed and also grant Swain a Soul Fragment.

SWAIN.name: NEVERMOVE
SWAIN.description: Swain launches a wave of demonic power forward. It then returns to Swain and roots enemies it hits. Swain can then choose to pull all rooted champions closer.

SWAIN.name: DEMONIC ASCENSION
SWAIN.description: Swain transforms into a demon and drains health from nearby enemy champions, minions, and neutral monsters. Swain can cast Demonflare to decimate and slow nearby enemies with a nova of soulfire. This form is indefinite as long as Swain drains enemy champions.

SYNDRA.name: TRANSCENDENT
SYNDRA.description: Syndra collects Splinters of Wrath by dealing ability damage to enemies and every time she levels up an ability. Splinters of Wrath can be used to upgrade her abilities and increase ability power.

SYNDRA.name: DARK SPHERE
SYNDRA.description: Syndra conjures a Dark Sphere that deals magic damage where it appears. The sphere remains and can be manipulated by her other powers. Upgrade: Syndra gains an additional charge of Dark Sphere.

SYNDRA.name: FORCE OF WILL
SYNDRA.description: Syndra hurls the nearest Dark Sphere at a target location, dealing magic damage and slowing the Move Speed of enemies within the area. Upgrade: Syndra deals bonus true damage.

SYNDRA.name: SCATTER THE WEAK
SYNDRA.description: Syndra sends out a wave of force, dealing magic damage and knocking back enemies and Dark Spheres. Enemies hit by Dark Spheres are stunned and take additional damage. Upgrade: Syndra increases the range of the wave of force.

SYNDRA.name: UNLEASHED POWER
SYNDRA.description: Syndra launches the Dark Spheres orbiting her and any nearby at an enemy champion, dealing magic damage for each Sphere. Upgrade: The Dark Spheres execute enemies with low Health. When killing an enemy, the Spheres will explode on the spot and deal damage to nearby enemy champions.

TALON.name: BLADE'S END
TALON.description: Talon's spells Wound champions and large monsters, stacking up to 3 times. When Talon attacks a champion with 3 stacks of Wound, they bleed for heavy damage over time.

TALON.name: NOXIAN DIPLOMACY
TALON.description: Talon stabs the target unit. If they are within melee range, this attack deals critical damage. If they are outside melee range, Talon will leap at his target before stabbing them. Talon refunds some health and cooldown if this ability kills the target.

TALON.name: RAKE
TALON.description: Talon sends out a volley of daggers that then return back to him, dealing physical damage every time it passes through an enemy. The returning blades deal bonus damage and slow units hit.

TALON.name: ASSASSIN'S PATH
TALON.description: Talon vaults over any terrain or structure, up to a max distance. This ability has a low cooldown, but puts the used terrain on a long cooldown.

TALON.name: SHADOW ASSAULT
TALON.description: Talon disperses a ring of blades and becomes Invisible while gaining additional Move Speed. When Talon emerges from Invisibility, the blades converge on his location. Each time the blades move, Shadow Assault deals physical damage to enemies hit by at least one blade.

TEEMO.name: TOXIC SHOT
TEEMO.description: Teemo's attacks deal bonus magic damage over time.

TEEMO.name: BLINDING DART
TEEMO.description: Teemo fires a dart that blinds its target, causing its attacks to deal no damage for a brief period.

TEEMO.name: MOVE QUICK
TEEMO.description: Teemo scampers around, passively increasing his Movement Speed until he is struck by an enemy champion or turret. Activating Move Quick causes Teemo to roll forward a short distance, sprinting for a few seconds. During this time, Move Quick's passive speed is doubled, and cannot be removed by damage.

TEEMO.name: GUERILLA WARFARE
TEEMO.description: After a delay, Teemo becomes camouflaged, unable to be seen unless near an enemy champion or turret. After exiting camouflage, Teemo gains Attack Speed.

TEEMO.name: NOXIOUS TRAP
TEEMO.description: Teemo throws an explosive poisonous trap using one of the mushrooms stored in his pack. If an enemy steps on the trap, it will release a poisonous puddle, slowing enemies and damaging them over time. If Teemo throws a mushroom onto another mushroom it will bounce, gaining additional range.

THRESH.name: DAMNATION
THRESH.description: Thresh can harvest the souls of enemies that die near him, permanently granting him Armor and Ability Power.

THRESH.name: DEATH SENTENCE
THRESH.description: Thresh binds an enemy in chains and pulls them toward him. Activating this ability a second time pulls Thresh to the enemy.

THRESH.name: DARK PASSAGE
THRESH.description: Throws a Lantern to a target location. If an ally collects it Thresh will pull the ally to him.

THRESH.name: FLAY
THRESH.description: Thresh's attacks wind up, dealing more damage the longer he waits between attacks. When activated, Thresh sweeps his chain, knocking all enemies hit in the direction of the blow.

THRESH.name: THE BOX
THRESH.description: A prison of walls that slow and deal damage if broken.

TRISTANA.name: DRAW A BEAD
TRISTANA.description: Increases Tristana's range for her attacks, Explosive Charge, and Buster Shot as she levels.

TRISTANA.name: RAPID FIRE
TRISTANA.description: Tristana increases her Attack Speed for a short time.

TRISTANA.name: ROCKET JUMP
TRISTANA.description: Tristana fires at the ground to propel her to a distant location, dealing damage and slowing surrounding units for a brief period where she lands. Takedowns and fully stacked Explosive Charge detonations on champions reset Rocket Jump's cooldown.

TRISTANA.name: EXPLOSIVE CHARGE
TRISTANA.description: When Tristana kills a unit, her cannonballs burst into shrapnel, dealing damage to surrounding enemies. Can be activated to place a bomb on a target enemy or turret that explodes after a short duration dealing damage to surrounding units.

TRISTANA.name: BUSTER SHOT
TRISTANA.description: Tristana loads a massive cannonball into her weapon and fires it at an enemy unit. This deals Magic Damage and knocks the target back.

TRYNDAMERE.name: BATTLE FURY
TRYNDAMERE.description: Tryndamere gains Fury for each attack, critical strike, and killing blow he makes. Fury passively increases his Critical Strike Chance and can be consumed with his Bloodlust spell.

TRYNDAMERE.name: BLOODLUST
TRYNDAMERE.description: Tryndamere thrives on the thrills of combat, increasing his Attack Damage as he is more and more wounded. He can cast Bloodlust to consume his Fury and heal himself.

TRYNDAMERE.name: MOCKING SHOUT
TRYNDAMERE.description: Tryndamere lets out an insulting cry, decreasing surrounding champions' Attack Damage. Enemies with their backs turned to Tryndamere also have their Movement Speed reduced.

TRYNDAMERE.name: SPINNING SLASH
TRYNDAMERE.description: Tryndamere slices toward a target unit, dealing damage to enemies in his path.

TRYNDAMERE.name: UNDYING RAGE
TRYNDAMERE.description: Tryndamere's lust for battle becomes so strong that he is unable to die, no matter how wounded he becomes.

TWISTED_FATE.name: LOADED DICE
TWISTED_FATE.description: Upon killing a unit, Twisted Fate rolls his 'lucky' dice receiving bonus gold.

TWISTED_FATE.name: WILD CARDS
TWISTED_FATE.description: Twisted Fate throws three cards, dealing damage to each enemy unit they pass through.

TWISTED_FATE.name: PICK A CARD
TWISTED_FATE.description: Twisted Fate chooses a magic card from his deck, and uses that for his next attack, causing bonus effects. Red Cards deal damage in an area and slow, Blue Cards deal damage and restore mana, and Gold Cards deal damage and stun.

TWISTED_FATE.name: STACKED DECK
TWISTED_FATE.description: Every 4 attacks, Twisted Fate deals bonus damage. Activating this skill increases his Attack Speed, and attacking enemy champions rolls his Loaded Dice.

TWISTED_FATE.name: DESTINY
TWISTED_FATE.description: Twisted Fate predicts the fortunes of his foes, revealing all enemy champions and enabling the use of Gate, which teleports Twisted Fate to any target location in 1.5 seconds.

TWITCH.name: DEADLY VENOM
TWITCH.description: Twitch's basic attacks infect the target, dealing true damage each second.

TWITCH.name: AMBUSH
TWITCH.description: Twitch becomes Camouflaged for a short duration and gains Move Speed. When leaving Camouflage, Twitch gains Attack Speed for a short duration. When an enemy champion with Deadly Venom dies, Ambush's cooldown is reset.

TWITCH.name: VENOM CASK
TWITCH.description: Twitch hurls a cask of venom that explodes in an area, slowing targets and applying deadly venom to the target.

TWITCH.name: CONTAMINATE
TWITCH.description: Twitch wreaks further havoc on poisoned enemies with a blast of his vile diseases.

TWITCH.name: SPRAY AND PRAY
TWITCH.description: Twitch unleashes the full power of his crossbow, shooting bolts over a great distance that pierce all enemies caught in their path.

URGOT.name: ECHOING FLAMES
URGOT.description: Urgot's basic attacks and Purge periodically trigger blasts of flame from his legs, dealing physical damage.

URGOT.name: CORROSIVE CHARGE
URGOT.description: Fires an explosive charge at the target location, dealing physical damage and slowing enemies caught in the explosion.

URGOT.name: PURGE
URGOT.description: Urgot slows himself while he unloads his weapon on nearby enemies. Prioritizes enemy champions Urgot has recently struck with other abilities and triggers Echoing Flames.

URGOT.name: DISDAIN
URGOT.description: Urgot charges in a direction, shielding himself and trampling non-champion enemies. If he catches an enemy champion, he will stop and hurl them out of his way.

URGOT.name: FEAR BEYOND DEATH
URGOT.description: Urgot fires a chem-drill that impales the first enemy champion hit. If that champion falls below a health threshold, Urgot judges them weak and can execute them.

VARUS.name: LIVING VENGEANCE
VARUS.description: On kill or assist, Varus temporarily gains Attack Speed. This bonus is larger if the enemy is a champion.

VARUS.name: PIERCING ARROW
VARUS.description: Varus readies and then fires a powerful shot that gains extra range and damage the longer he spends preparing to fire.

VARUS.name: BLIGHTED QUIVER
VARUS.description: Passive: Varus' basic attacks deal bonus magic damage and apply Blight. Varus' other abilities detonate Blight, dealing magic damage based on the target's maximum Health. Active: Varus empowers his next Piercing Arrow.

VARUS.name: HAIL OF ARROWS
VARUS.description: Varus fires a hail of arrows that deal physical damage and desecrate the ground. Desecrated ground slows enemies' Movement Speed and reduces their self healing and regeneration.

VARUS.name: CHAIN OF CORRUPTION
VARUS.description: Varus flings out a damaging tendril of corruption that immobilizes the first enemy champion hit and then spreads towards nearby uninfected champions, immobilizing them too on contact.

VAYNE.name: NIGHT HUNTER
VAYNE.description: Vayne ruthlessly hunts evil-doers, gaining 30 Move Speed when moving toward nearby enemy champions.

VAYNE.name: TUMBLE
VAYNE.description: Vayne tumbles, maneuvering to carefully place her next shot. Her next attack deals bonus damage.

VAYNE.name: SILVER BOLTS
VAYNE.description: Vayne tips her bolts with a rare metal, toxic to evil things. The third consecutive attack or ability against the same target deals a percentage of the target's max health as bonus true damage. Activating this ability gives Vayne bonus Attack Speed and she heals for some of Silver Bolts' damage.

VAYNE.name: CONDEMN
VAYNE.description: Vayne draws a heavy crossbow from her back, and fires a huge bolt at her target, knocking them back and dealing damage. If they collide with terrain, they are impaled, dealing bonus damage and stunning them.

VAYNE.name: FINAL HOUR
VAYNE.description: Readying herself for an epic confrontation, Vayne gains increased Attack Damage, Invisibility during Tumble, and more bonus Movement Speed from Night Hunter. When an enemy champion damaged by Vayne dies within a few seconds, Final Hour's duration is extended.

VEIGAR.name: PHENOMENAL EVIL POWER
VEIGAR.description: Veigar now gains passive stacks by hitting enemy champions once again.

VEIGAR.name: BALEFUL STRIKE
VEIGAR.description: Veigar unleashes a bolt of dark energy that deals magic damage to the first two enemies hit. Units killed by this bolt grant Veigar some ability power permanently.

VEIGAR.name: DARK MATTER
VEIGAR.description: Veigar calls a great mass of dark matter to fall from the sky to the target location, dealing magic damage when it lands. Stacks of Phenomenal Evil reduce Dark Matter's cooldown.

VEIGAR.name: EVENT HORIZON
VEIGAR.description: Veigar twists the edges of space, creating a cage that Stuns enemies that pass through.

VEIGAR.name: PRIMORDIAL BURST
VEIGAR.description: Blasts target enemy champion, dealing a large amount of magic damage, increasing based on the target's missing health.

VEX.name: DOOM 'N GLOOM
VEX.description: Vex periodically becomes empowered, causing her next basic Ability to fear enemies and interrupt dashes. Whenever a nearby enemy dashes, Vex applies a mark that can be consumed for bonus damage that also reduces the cooldown of her empowered state.

VEX.name: MISTRAL BOLT
VEX.description: Launch a damaging missile that accelerates mid-flight.

VEX.name: PERSONAL SPACE
VEX.description: Gain a shield and damage nearby enemies.

VEX.name: LOOMING DARKNESS
VEX.description: Summon a damaging and slowing zone that applies Gloom to enemies.

VEX.name: SHADOW SURGE
VEX.description: Fire a missile that marks an enemy champion. Recast to dash to them and deal damage.

VI.name: DENTING BLOWS
VI.description: Every third attack on the same enemy deals a percentage of their maximum Health, reduces their Armor, and grants Vi Attack Speed.

VI.name: VAULT BREAKER
VI.description: Vi charges her gauntlets and unleashes a vault shattering punch, carrying her forward. Enemies she hits are knocked back and receive a stack of Denting Blows.

VI.name: BLAST SHIELD
VI.description: Vi gains stacks of Blast Shield when hitting an enemy with an attack or ability. Activating Blast Shield generates a shield that absorbs damage. At maximum stacks, Vi also gains Movement Speed.

VI.name: EXCESSIVE FORCE
VI.description: Vi's next attack blasts through her target, dealing damage to enemies behind it.

VI.name: ASSAULT AND BATTERY
VI.description: Vi runs down an enemy, knocking aside anyone in the way. When she reaches her target she knocks it into the air, jumps after it, and slams it back into the ground.

VIEGO.name: SOVEREIGN'S DOMINATION
VIEGO.description: Enemies who fall before Viego become wraiths. By attacking a wraith, Viego temporarily seizes control of the dead enemy's body, healing for a percentage of his target's max health and gaining access to their basic abilities and items. He replaces their Ultimate with a free cast of his own.

VIEGO.name: BLADE OF THE RUINED KING
VIEGO.description: Viego's spectral blade passively deals bonus percent current Health damage On-Hit and strikes twice vs. enemies he recently hit with an Ability, stealing Health. Viego can activate this Ability to thrust his zweihander forward, impaling enemies in front of him.

VIEGO.name: SPECTRAL MAW
VIEGO.description: Viego charges up before dashing forward, releasing a ball of concentrated Black Mist that stuns the first enemy hit.

VIEGO.name: HARROWED PATH
VIEGO.description: Viego commands the Black Mist to haunt and surround a piece of terrain. Viego can hide in the Mist as a wraith, gaining camouflage, Move Speed, and Attack Speed.

VIEGO.name: HEARTBREAKER
VIEGO.description: Viego teleports to a nearby location and executes an enemy champion on arrival, piercing their heart and causing a destructive shockwave around them that knocks away their allies.

VLADIMIR.name: CRIMSON PACT
VLADIMIR.description: Every 30 points of bonus Health gives Vladimir 1 Ability Power and every 1 point of Ability Power gives Vladimir 1.6 bonus Health (does not stack with itself).

VLADIMIR.name: TRANSFUSION
VLADIMIR.description: Vladimir steals life from the target enemy. When Vladimir's resource is full, Transfusion will benefit from massively increased damage and healing for a brief time.

VLADIMIR.name: SANGUINE POOL
VLADIMIR.description: Vladimir sinks into a pool of blood, becoming untargetable for 2 seconds. Additionally, enemies on the pool are slowed and Vladimir siphons life from them.

VLADIMIR.name: TIDES OF BLOOD
VLADIMIR.description: Vladimir pays his own health to charge up a reservoir of blood which, when released, deals damage in the area around him but can be blocked by enemy units.

VLADIMIR.name: HEMOPLAGUE
VLADIMIR.description: Vladimir infects an area with a virulent plague. Affected enemies take increased damage for the duration. After a few seconds, Hemoplague deals magic damage to infected enemies and heals Vladimir for each enemy Champion hit.

VOLIBEAR.name: THE RELENTLESS STORM
VOLIBEAR.description: Volibear's Attacks and abilities grant Attack Speed, and eventually cause his Attacks to deal bonus magic damage to nearby enemies.

VOLIBEAR.name: THUNDERING SMASH
VOLIBEAR.description: Volibear gains speed towards enemies, Stunning and damaging the first one he Attacks.

VOLIBEAR.name: FRENZIED MAUL
VOLIBEAR.description: Volibear damages an enemy, applying on-hit effects and gaining a mark. Casting this ability again on the same target consumes the mark to deal bonus damage and heal Volibear.

VOLIBEAR.name: SKY SPLITTER
VOLIBEAR.description: Volibear summons a lightning bolt at a location, dealing damage and Slowing enemies while granting Volibear a shield if he's inside the blast radius.

VOLIBEAR.name: STORMBRINGER
VOLIBEAR.description: Volibear leaps to a target location, Slowing and damaging enemies beneath him while gaining bonus Health. Enemy towers near his landing location become temporarily disabled.

WARWICK.name: ETERNAL HUNGER
WARWICK.description: Warwick's basic attacks deal bonus magic damage. If Warwick is below 50% health, he heals for the same amount.

WARWICK.name: JAWS OF THE BEAST
WARWICK.description: Warwick lunges forward and bites his target, dealing damage based on their maximum health and healing for damage dealt.

WARWICK.name: BLOODHUNT
WARWICK.description: Warwick senses enemies below 50% health, gaining Move Speed toward and Attack Speed against them. When they fall below 20% health, he frenzies and these bonuses triple.

WARWICK.name: PRIMAL HOWL
WARWICK.description: Warwick gains damage reduction for 2.5 seconds. At the end, or if re-activated, he howls, causing nearby enemies to flee for 1 second.

WARWICK.name: INFINITE DURESS
WARWICK.description: Warwick leaps in a direction (scaling with his bonus Move Speed), suppressing the first champion he collides with for 1.5 seconds.

WUKONG.name: CRUSHING BLOWS
WUKONG.description: Wukong and his clones' attacks and abilities apply stacks of Crushing Blows. For each stack, Wukong and his clones deal increased damage to the target.

WUKONG.name: GOLDEN STAFF
WUKONG.description: Passively gives Wukong's next attack bonus range after casting an ability. Wukong's next attack deals additional damage and heals him.

WUKONG.name: WARRIOR TRICKSTER
WUKONG.description: Wukong becomes Invisible and dashes in a direction, leaving behind a clone that will attack enemies for reduced damage, mimicking Golden Staff and Cyclone.

WUKONG.name: NIMBUS STRIKE
WUKONG.description: Wukong dashes to a targeted enemy and sends out images to attack enemies near his target, dealing damage to each enemy struck, and grants Wukong a temporary Attack Speed increase.

WUKONG.name: CYCLONE
WUKONG.description: Wukong extends his staff and spins it around repeatedly, gaining Movement Speed. Enemies struck take damage and are knocked up. Cyclone can be recast within a short time window.

XAYAH.name: CLEAN CUTS
XAYAH.description: After using an ability, Xayah's next basic attacks will hit all targets along their path and leave a Feather. Lover's Leap: Xayah can join Rakan's recall.

XAYAH.name: DOUBLE DAGGERS
XAYAH.description: Xayah throws two damaging daggers that also drop Feathers she can recall.

XAYAH.name: DEADLY PLUMAGE
XAYAH.description: Xayah creates a storm of blades that increase her basic attack speed and damage while granting her movement speed if she attacks a champion. If an ally Rakan is nearby, he also gains the effects of this ability.

XAYAH.name: BLADECALLER
XAYAH.description: Xayah calls back all her dropped Feathers dealing damage and rooting enemies if hit with 3 or more.

XAYAH.name: FEATHERSTORM
XAYAH.description: Xayah leaps into the air becoming untargetable and throwing out a fan of daggers, dropping Feathers she can recall.

XIN_ZHAO.name: DETERMINATION
XIN_ZHAO.description: Every third attack deals bonus damage and heals Xin Zhao.

XIN_ZHAO.name: THREE TALON STRIKE
XIN_ZHAO.description: Xin Zhao's next 3 standard attacks deal increased damage with the third attack knocking an opponent into the air.

XIN_ZHAO.name: WIND BECOMES LIGHTNING
XIN_ZHAO.description: Xin Zhao slashes in front of himself with his spear, then thrusts it forward, slowing affected enemies.

XIN_ZHAO.name: AUDACIOUS CHARGE
XIN_ZHAO.description: Xin Zhao charges to an enemy, dealing damage to all enemies in the area and slowing them briefly.

XIN_ZHAO.name: CRESCENT GUARD
XIN_ZHAO.description: Xin Zhao deals damage to nearby enemies based on their current Health and knocks non-challenged targets back. Xin Zhao is impervious to damage dealt by champions outside of the circle created.

YASUO.name: WAY OF THE WANDERER
YASUO.description: Yasuo's Critical Strike Chance is doubled. Additionally, Yasuo builds toward a shield whenever he is moving. The shield triggers when he takes damage from a champion or monster.

YASUO.name: STEEL TEMPEST
YASUO.description: Thrusts forward, damaging all enemies in a line. On hit, grants a stack of Gathering Storm for a few seconds. At 2 stacks, Steel Tempest fires a whirlwind that knocks Airborne. Steel Tempest is treated as a basic attack and scales with all the same things.

YASUO.name: WIND WALL
YASUO.description: Creates a moving wall that blocks all enemy projectiles for 4 seconds.

YASUO.name: SWEEPING BLADE
YASUO.description: Dashes through target enemy, dealing magic damage. Each cast increases your next dash's base Damage, up to a max amount. Cannot be re-cast on the same enemy for a few seconds. If Steel Tempest is cast while dashing, it will strike as a circle.

YASUO.name: LAST BREATH
YASUO.description: Blinks to an Airborne enemy champion, dealing physical damage and holding all Airborne enemies in the area in the air. Grants maximum Flow but resets all stacks of Gathering Storm. For a moderate time afterwards, Yasuo's critical strikes gain significant Bonus Armor Penetration.

YONE.name: WAY OF THE HUNTER
YONE.description: Yone deals magic damage with every second Attack. In addition, his critical strike chance is increased.

YONE.name: MORTAL STEEL
YONE.description: Thrusts forward, damaging all enemies in a line. On hit, grants a stack of Gathering Storm for a few seconds. At 2 stacks, Mortal Steel causes Yone to dash forward with a gust of wind, knocking enemies Airborne. Mortal Steel is treated as a basic Attack and scales with all the same things.

YONE.name: SPIRIT CLEAVE
YONE.description: Cleaves forward, damaging all enemies in a cone. Grants a shield to Yone. The shield's value is increased by the number of champions hit. Spirit Cleave's cooldown and cast time scale with Attack Speed.

YONE.name: SOUL UNBOUND
YONE.description: Yone's spirit leaves his body behind, gaining Move Speed. When this skill ends, Yone's spirit is forced back to his body and he repeats a portion of the damage he dealt as a spirit.

YONE.name: FATE SEALED
YONE.description: Yone blinks behind the last champion in a line with a slash so powerful it pulls all enemies hit towards him.

YUUMI.name: BOP 'N' BLOCK
YUUMI.description: Periodically, when Yuumi attacks a champion, she restores mana and gains a shield that follows her, protecting her and the ally she's attached to.

YUUMI.name: PROWLING PROJECTILE
YUUMI.description: Yuumi fires a missile, dealing damage to the first target hit. It deals bonus damage and slows if it takes at least 1 second to get to its target. While Attached, the missile can be controlled with your cursor.

YUUMI.name: YOU AND ME!
YUUMI.description: Passively, Yuumi increases her ally's Adaptive Force and her own. Actively, Yuumi dashes to a target ally, becoming untargetable from everything except turrets.

YUUMI.name: ZOOMIES
YUUMI.description: Heals Yuumi and boosts Movement Speed and Attack Speed. If she's attached, she passes it to her ally instead.

YUUMI.name: FINAL CHAPTER
YUUMI.description: Yuumi channels seven waves of damage, rooting anyone hit by three or more. Yuumi can move, attach, and cast Zoomies! while channeling.

ZED.name: CONTEMPT FOR THE WEAK
ZED.description: Zed's basic attacks against low health targets deals bonus Magic Damage. This effect can only occur once every few seconds on the same target.

ZED.name: RAZOR SHURIKEN
ZED.description: Zed and his shadows throw their shurikens. Each shuriken deals damage to every enemy hit.

ZED.name: LIVING SHADOW
ZED.description: Passive: Zed gains energy whenever he and his shadows strike an enemy with the same ability. Energy can only be gained once per cast ability. Active: Zed's shadow dashes forward, remaining in place for a few seconds. Reactivating Living Shadow will cause Zed to switch positions with this shadow.

ZED.name: SHADOW SLASH
ZED.description: Zed and his shadows slash, dealing damage to nearby enemies.

ZED.name: DEATH MARK
ZED.description: Zed becomes untargetable and dashes to an enemy champion, marking them. After a few seconds the mark triggers, repeating a portion of all the damage Zed dealt to the target while they were marked. Zed leaves a shadow behind and can reactive Death Mark to switch places with this shadow.

ZERI.name: LIVING BATTERY
ZERI.description: Zeri gains Move Speed whenever she receives a shield. When she damages an enemy shield she absorbs its energy, shielding herself.

ZERI.name: ELECTROCUTE!
ZERI.description: Zeri's Attacks are treated as Abilities and Electrocute! is treated as an Attack. Moving and casting Electrocute! stores up energy in Zeri's Sparkpack. When fully charged her next Attack will slow and deal bonus damage. Electrocute! shoots a burst of 7 rounds that deal attack damage to the first enemy hit.

ZERI.name: ULTRASHOCK LASER
ZERI.description: Zeri fires an electric pulse that slows and damages the first enemy hit. If the pulse hits a wall it expands into a long range laser.

ZERI.name: SPARK SURGE
ZERI.description: Zeri dashes a short distance and energizes her next 3 shots of Burst Fire, causing them to pierce through enemies. She will vault and grind over any terrain she touches.

ZERI.name: LIGHTNING CRASH
ZERI.description: Zeri discharges a nova of electricity and overcharges herself, gaining increased damage and stacking Move Speed that refreshes and gets stronger every time she hits an enemy champion. While overcharged, Burst fire becomes a faster triple shot that chains lightning between enemies.

ZIGGS.name: SHORT FUSE
ZIGGS.description: All of Ziggs’s abilities also damage structures. Periodically, his next ability deals bonus magic damage. This cooldown is reduced whenever Ziggs uses an ability.

ZIGGS.name: BOUNCING BOMB
ZIGGS.description: Ziggs throws a bouncing bomb that deals magic damage.

ZIGGS.name: SATCHEL CHARGE
ZIGGS.description: Ziggs flings an explosive charge that detonates after 4 seconds, or when this ability is activated again. The explosion deals magic damage to enemies, knocking them away. Ziggs is also knocked away, but takes no damage. Ziggs can use the Satchel to hexplode vulnerable enemy turrets.

ZIGGS.name: HEXPLOSIVE MINEFIELD
ZIGGS.description: Ziggs scatters proximity mines that detonate on enemy contact, dealing magic damage and slowing. Successive mine detonations on the same target deal reduced damage.

ZIGGS.name: MEGA INFERNO BOMB
ZIGGS.description: Ziggs deploys his ultimate creation, the Mega Inferno Bomb, hurling it an enormous distance. Enemies in the primary blast zone take more damage than those farther away. When quick casting, the bomb will target the enemy with the lowest HP.

ZOE.name: MORE SPARKLES!
ZOE.description: Zoe's next basic attack after casting a spell deals bonus magic damage.

ZOE.name: PADDLE STAR!
ZOE.description: Zoe fires a missile that she can redirect in flight. Deals more damage the longer it flies in a straight line.

ZOE.name: SPELL THIEF
ZOE.description: Zoe can pick up the remnants of enemy summoner spell and active item casts and cast them once herself. Whenever she casts a summoner spell, she gains 3 missiles that fire at the nearest target.

ZOE.name: SLEEPY TROUBLE BUBBLE
ZOE.description: Causes the target to become drowsy, then fall asleep. The first source of damage that breaks the sleep is doubled, up to a cap.

ZOE.name: PORTAL JUMP
ZOE.description: Blink to a nearby position for 1 second. Then blink back.

ZYRA.name: GARDEN OF THORNS
ZYRA.description: When hitting enemies with Deadly Spines or Grasping Roots, Zyra spawns Thorn Spitters who fight for her.

ZYRA.name: DEADLY SPINES
ZYRA.description: Thick vines spread through the ground and explode into spines, dealing magic damage to enemies within the area. Zyra will also spawn a Thorn Spitter, dealing damage. For each enemy hit the number of Thorn Spitters will increase.

ZYRA.name: RAMPANT GROWTH
ZYRA.description: Zyra plants a seed on an enemy champion, dealing damage over time and slowing them down. Thorn Spitters in the area will deal bonus damage on marked enemy champions.

ZYRA.name: GRASPING ROOTS
ZYRA.description: Zyra sends forth vines through the ground to ensnare her target, dealing damage and rooting enemies they come across. Zyra spawns a Thorn Spitter when the vines hit the first enemy, or after the skill is cast if no enemy is hit.

ZYRA.name: STRANGLETHORNS
ZYRA.description: Zyra summons a twisted thicket at her target location, dealing damage to enemies as it expands and knocking them airborne as it contracts. Plants within the thicket are enraged.
